(14, 5, 'ni menunjukkan bahwa pandemi COVID-19 tidak hanya mengancam kesehatan fisik, tetapi juga mengganggu stabilitas emosional, sosial dan ekonomi keluarga. Oleh karena itu, diperlukan kebijakan yang komprehensif dan program bantuan sosial serta pemberian modal tambahan bagi pelaku UMKM yang efektif untuk membantu keluarga yang terdampak dalam menghadapi dampak jangka panjang dari pandemi COVID-19 sehingga mereka dapat bertahan . Kata Kunci: COVID-19, dampak ekonomi, dampak sosial, kesejahteraan keluarga, pandemi , UMKM Pendahuluan Pandemi COVID-19 yang mulai m asuk di Indonesia pada awal tahun 2020 telah me ngakibatkan dampak yang luar biasa terhadap berbagai aspek kehidupan masyarakat.', '[0.5109190344810486,0.5194122195243835,-3.247843027114868,0.3367060124874115,0.9338900446891785,0.6787999868392944,0.5827745199203491,-1.0443180799484253,1.1270860433578491,0.016885440796613693,0.17474907636642456,-0.39774051308631897,1.3474457263946533,0.7415754795074463,0.35747402906417847,-0.14577160775661469,-0.567224383354187,0.016823971644043922,-1.4113926887512207,1.2831984758377075,-0.7876175045967102,0.43145087361335754,-0.4534267783164978,-0.937709391117096,0.9450653195381165,0.4668411612510681,0.06114792823791504,0.4536575675010681,-0.20786887407302856,-1.0825411081314087,0.17198850214481354,-0.2020220011472702,-0.6443758010864258,-0.7501856088638306,0.3231795132160187,-0.978999137878418,1.3342465162277222,-0.053628966212272644,0.23844346404075623,-0.8712737560272217,0.19587069749832153,-0.41388317942619324,1.0481271743774414,-0.4040364623069763,0.6757968664169312,0.585448145866394,0.9648929834365845,1.3232964277267456,-0.1876111477613449,-0.9133657813072205,-0.45443397760391235,-1.3278703689575195,0.18237946927547455,-0.34944695234298706,0.19514457881450653,0.3193090260028839,-0.8012765645980835,0.1321396678686142,-0.25175994634628296,-0.2733669877052307,1.6896744966506958,0.9086686968803406,-0.8085464239120483,0.4389927387237549,0.5254544615745544,-0.1698604226112