(28, 5, 'daring dan pekerjaan jarak jauh. Mengintegrasikan layanan kesehatan mental ke dalam program penanganan pandemi, termasuk penyediaan konseling daring. Untuk Masyarakat Meningkatkan solidaritas sosial melalui inisiatif lokal seperti bank makanan, pendampingan belajar anak, atau layanan berbagi informasi kerja. Memanfaatkan teknologi untuk menciptakan peluang ekonomi baru, seperti usaha berbasis digital atau penjualan online . Astuti, S., &amp; Pratiwi, L. (2020). Ketahanan Keluarga dalam Menghadapi Pandemi COVID-19 di Indonesia. Jurnal Psikologi Sosial, 18(3), 45-58. Diah Widiawati Retnoningtias , (2024) Psikologi Keluarga : Makasar . TOHAR MEDIA Euis Sunarti . (2021) Ketahanan keluarga Indonesia di masa pandemi Covid-19 , Bogor: PT IPB Press Handayani, T., &amp; Nugroho, S. (2021). Adaptasi Ekonomi Keluarga selama Pandemi COVID-19: Studi Kasus di Jawa Tengah. Jurnal Ekonomi Indonesia, 15(1), 10-22. Hardiyati .', '[0.5769345760345459,0.980331540107727,-3.3290772438049316,0.22867755591869354,0.3603280782699585,0.3645918071269989,0.3055121898651123,-1.0823471546173096,0.7989411354064941,-0.24183709919452667,-0.2306690514087677,-0.6302241086959839,0.9502086639404297,0.6551032662391663,0.2893800139427185,-0.22433388233184814,-0.05210927128791809,-0.49809861183166504,-1.4532968997955322,0.573474109172821,-1.2447123527526855,0.09013254940509796,-0.5195565819740295,-0.12632066011428833,0.48577460646629333,-0.00790360290557146,-0.5967293977737427,-0.3486176133155823,-0.2603074908256531,0.039409905672073364,0.12030281126499176,-0.03741275519132614,-0.9999229907989502,-0.3694259226322174,0.4693782925605774,-0.4498172998428345,1.2424689531326294,0.08958413451910019,-0.25229954719543457,-0.7012217044830322,0.08385259658098221,0.1175023540854454,0.035154059529304504,-0.7333673238754272,0.8243263363838196,0.3431185483932495,0.831600546836853,0.7841049432754517,0.8369128108024597,-0.9807239770889282,-0.27931734919548035,-1.1841572523117065,0.751802921295166,-0.1603254824876